title: Bug 121682: Exception throws when exporting data from a table containing highlights/maps
description: Description: An exception is thrown when attempting to export data from the attached report.
OB: When attempting to export data from a table that contains a group row, highlight rule, and map rule, an exception is thrown.
EB: The application should not throw an exception when exporting data from a table that contains highlights/maps.
SR: To reproduce the issue: 1. Add a table to the report that contains a group row, highlight rule, and map rule. 2. Preview the report. 3. Attempt to export the data.
